OL,3,CTrump sharply escalates feud with the
OL,4,CBBC - demanding up to $5bn
OL,6,FITV News Correspondent Robert Moore
OL,7,Freports on the latest developments in
OL,8,FPresident Trump's legal battle against
OL,9,Fthe BBC.
OL,11,FDonald Trump has arrived in Florida
OL,12,Ffor the weekend, still determined to
OL,13,Fpursue legal action against the BBC.
OL,15,FNot only has he declared that the BBC
OL,16,Fapology and retraction are
OL,17,Finsufficient, Trump is now suggesting
OL,18,Fthat he will sue the corporation for
OL,19,Fup to $5 billion - five times his
OL,20,Foriginal figure.
