OL,3,CTrump sharply escalates feud with the
OL,4,CBBC - demanding up to $5bn
OL,6,FThe BBC has made clear that it is not
OL,7,Fprepared to pay the president
OL,8,Fcompensation, arguing that it made a
OL,9,Fmistake, but that the Panorama
OL,10,Fdocumentary, which was broadcast just
OL,11,Fdays before the 2024 election, was not
OL,12,Fdefamatory.
OL,14,FTrump issued his renewed legal threats
OL,15,Fin two interviews. The first was to GB
OL,16,FNews in the White House last night. He
OL,17,Finsisted that the BBC editing of the
OL,18,Fdocumentary was so misleading and
OL,19,F"egregious" that he felt an
OL,20,F"obligation" to sue the company.
