OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThen later, speaking aboard Air Force
OL,12,FOne, he told reporters that he would
OL,13,Fsue for between "one to five billion
OL,14,Fdollars" and would likely file the
OL,15,Flawsuit at some point next week.
OL,17,FTrump added that he wants to speak to
OL,18,FKeir Starmer this weekend, who he said
OL,19,Fwas embarrassed by the whole affair,
OL,20,Fand he suggested that UK taxpayers are
OL,21,F"very angry" with the BBC.
