OL,3,CTrump sharply escalates feud with the
OL,4,CBBC - demanding up to $5bn
OL,6,FThere is no suggestion that the
OL,7,Fpresident's legal team will retreat
OL,8,Ffrom their threats. Trump described
OL,9,Fthe BBC News editing of his January 6,
OL,10,F2021, speech as "beyond fake, this is
OL,11,Fcorrupt".
OL,13,FThis piles pressure on BBC executives
OL,14,Fand the corporation's lawyers. They
OL,15,Fmust now reckon with the likelihood
OL,16,Fthat the lawsuit will go ahead,
OL,17,Fdespite the apology and retraction.
